00:00:47,610 --> 00:00:48,890
Episode 37

3
00:00:48,890 --> 00:00:55,090
From the beginning... From the start of this great cause,

4
00:00:55,090 --> 00:00:58,570
I didn't have any place in it, did I?

5
00:01:09,490 --> 00:01:15,070
That's right. From the start, there was no place for you in this great cause,

6
00:01:15,070 --> 00:01:20,150
but you eventually made one for yourself.

7
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:30,290
Killing Po Eun. That will become your place.

8
00:01:57,490 --> 00:02:02,530
What about Lord Po Eun? What happened to him?

9
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:07,210
Lord Po Eun died.

10
00:02:12,110 --> 00:02:17,450
Then, what about His Highness?

11
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:20,390
He's probably not in a good situation.

12
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:22,110
Is he alive?

13
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:24,910
He is probably alive.

14
00:02:26,250 --> 00:02:31,430
He will soon step down from the throne.

15
00:02:32,330 --> 00:02:34,610
That went well.

16
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:52,150
Why didn't you kill me?

17
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:56,830
You didn't kill me either.

18
00:03:00,050 --> 00:03:04,870
Last time at Byeokrando and at the market,

19
00:03:04,870 --> 00:03:08,030
you were more than capable of killing me.

20
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:16,730
Why do you live wielding a sword?

21
00:03:22,270 --> 00:03:26,610
I want to protect the people I love.

22
00:03:27,950 --> 00:03:32,690
I want to protect my dream.

23
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:41,630
I am the same. The person I love,

24
00:03:43,650 --> 00:03:45,290
dream...

25
00:03:49,670 --> 00:03:56,430
Are you going to avenge Lord Po Eun?

26
00:03:59,430 --> 00:04:02,030
I won't avenge.

27
00:04:03,190 --> 00:04:10,850
My dream is to go back to the time before His Highness went up to the throne.

28
00:04:12,550 --> 00:04:19,030
If it's not for Lord Po Eun, he probably wouldn't have taken the throne, right?

29
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:26,530
Just living a quiet life with His Highness,

30
00:04:27,890 --> 00:04:29,950
it's only that.

31
00:04:32,050 --> 00:04:40,890
If nobody hurts him, I won't fight anyone.

32
00:04:53,990 --> 00:04:56,030
Lady!

33
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:58,970
Now, Po Eun's head will be hung in the market,

34
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:03,530
and it must be officially announced that he's a traitor.

35
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:04,630
Sam Bong.

36
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:08,890
I tried to change the country through the support of the people,

37
00:05:08,890 --> 00:05:12,330
but the people's hearts, that we barely got a hold of through the land reform,

38
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,630
are now impossible to get back again due to Po Eun's death.

39
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:17,450
But to hang Po Eun's head—

40
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:20,970
What use is there to try turning back something that is irreversible?

41
00:05:22,850 --> 00:05:25,850
We have to quickly and strongly proceed with this.

42
00:05:25,850 --> 00:05:29,530
Dethroning the current king and as well as founding a new country.

43
00:05:29,530 --> 00:05:31,750
Do you all understand?

44
00:05:33,130 --> 00:05:38,750
Po Eun left like that and I don't even know if Yoon Rang is still alive.

45
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:41,970
This is the end.

46
00:05:41,970 --> 00:05:48,490
Your Highness! Jo Joon, Nam Eun, and Jeong Do Jeon are entering.

47
00:05:48,490 --> 00:05:50,790
Let them in.

48
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:08,930
Your Highness, Po Eun Jeong Mong Joo used sly tricks to falsely charge people with crimes, and

49
00:06:08,930 --> 00:06:16,150
he planned a conspiracy and received Your Highness' royal command to execute innocent people.

50
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:22,450
The reason why General Lee Seong Gye's fifth son, Lee Bang Won, attacked Jeong Mong Joo

51
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:25,090
was to stop a conspiracy.

52
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:30,310
So please hang Jeong Mong Joo's head in the commons

53
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:35,710
and give us the decree that denounces him as a traitor.

54
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:38,810
Please give us the command.

55
00:07:10,290 --> 00:07:13,950
Your grace is immeasurable.

56
00:07:20,750 --> 00:07:25,550
When are you going to take the royal seal?

57
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:36,570
There's an order for everything so please wait.

58
00:07:53,910 --> 00:07:57,150
I didn't want to become the king.

59
00:08:01,610 --> 00:08:04,530
Arrest all those people who are putting up false posters.

60
00:08:04,530 --> 00:08:05,350
Yes!

61
00:08:05,350 --> 00:08:07,150
Move aside!

62
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:25,090
His Highness has ordered for Traitor Jeong Mong Joo to be hanged.

63
00:08:25,090 --> 00:08:27,550
Those who will go against it

64
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:32,610
will also be treated as traitors and will be killed.

65
00:08:32,610 --> 00:08:34,610
Do you understand?

66
00:09:00,950 --> 00:09:03,550
I can become even stronger.

67
00:09:33,670 --> 00:09:36,630
Bang Ji's movements have changed.

68
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:40,310
He's following the Goksan swordsmanship.

69
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:44,190
Ah. Goksan swordsmanship.

70
00:09:47,410 --> 00:09:50,470
That's right. It's that.

71
00:09:53,210 --> 00:09:58,150
What are you doing here? Elder Sam Bong told everyone to gather.

72
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:01,350
I think it's because of what Young Master Bang Won did.

73
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:06,350
The market is going crazy wanting to execute Young Master Bang Won.

74
00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:10,250
Then, are they telling him to just sit down and die? They're too much.

75
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:13,350
They're waiting so hurry and go.

76
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:15,830
Master Hong, what are you doing? Hurry. Moo Hyul, go.

77
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:19,570
Let's not drag time now. We have to make haste.

78
00:10:19,570 --> 00:10:23,530
Yeon Hee, you have to spread rumors among the Sadaebu through Hwa Sa Dan.

79
00:10:23,530 --> 00:10:24,890
Please speak.

80
00:10:24,890 --> 00:10:28,290
After the General heard about Po Eun's death from Bang Won,

81
00:10:28,290 --> 00:10:32,250
he threw an inkstone at Bang Won and cracked his head.

82
00:10:35,910 --> 00:10:41,110
You said that wound came from your older brother, right?

83
00:10:41,110 --> 00:10:45,050
Spread a rumor that it was done by the General.

84
00:10:45,930 --> 00:10:50,750
Say that after doing that, the General cried for three days and nights.

85
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:55,970
The whole family was unable to sleep because of the General's sorrowful wailing. Do you understand?

86
00:10:55,970 --> 00:10:58,350
Yes. I understand.

87
00:10:58,350 --> 00:11:02,190
Boon Yi, you should also spread it through the market organization.

88
00:11:02,190 --> 00:11:07,210
Emphasize that it was solely done by Lee Bang Won.

89
00:11:10,040 --> 00:11:12,980
What do you mean?

90
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:17,080
We will now establish the new country.

91
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:22,160
Bang Won has be to excluded from this process.

92
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:29,130
The General, who will be leading the new country,

93
00:11:29,130 --> 00:11:35,170
has to be innocent of kiling Po Eun. It needs to be justified like that.

94
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:46,180
I don't really know much, but wasn't it done so that we can live?

95
00:11:46,180 --> 00:11:50,120
He did it to survive. Isn't that justification?

96
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:56,820
If we could do it using strength, then we could've just seized the palace on the day we attacked Jo Min Soo.

97
00:11:56,820 --> 00:12:00,520
Until now, even though it took time,

98
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:05,830
we put in so much effort in order to persuade, to debate and to embrace.

99
00:12:05,830 --> 00:12:07,640
But...

100
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:12,190
It has all become nothing now.

101
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:19,790
Even if it pains the heart, the new country was started with the sword.

102
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:24,330
Bang Won has to take responsibility for this in his own way and

103
00:12:24,330 --> 00:12:28,080
we have to proceed and endure it in our own way.

104
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,700
But Elder—

105
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:33,090
Bang Won, you understand, right?

106
00:12:33,090 --> 00:12:36,680
Yes. Of course.

107
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:40,140
That doesn't make sense!

108
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:44,950
It's right though. I was the one who killed Po Eun.

109
00:12:44,950 --> 00:12:48,590
I mean, did you kill him to gain fame and money?

110
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,370
Did you kill him to succeed?

111
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:54,210
Teacher Sam Bong didn't say to spread the rumor that, in order to gain fame and money,

112
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:59,310
I killed Teacher Po Eun. It wasn't worded like this.

113
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:11,770
I independently killed Po Eun.

114
00:13:11,770 --> 00:13:19,150
I, Lee Bang Won, killed Goryeo's last remaining loyalist, Jeong Mong Joo.

115
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:23,770
It is not connected in any way to General Lee Seong Gye.

116
00:13:23,770 --> 00:13:29,290
He said to spread it like this. There is nothing wrong with it.

117
00:13:29,290 --> 00:13:31,100
Still, Young Master...

118
00:13:31,100 --> 00:13:37,000
If I have to take responsibility for this, then let it be.

119
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:43,500
That's what makes me different from Sam Bong and Father. I will not avoid it.

120
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:12,770
I'm okay. You don't have to worry.

121
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:26,920
I heard about it.

122
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:34,280
A scandal and disgrace like that, you can just ignore it.

123
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:38,080
Just think of the future.

124
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,520
I am thinking of doing so.

125
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:47,380
Boon, look into who put up posters asking for me to be executed.

126
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:48,240
What?

127
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:52,440
What will you do? You must not.

128
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:56,060
Yes, Young Master. You have to be careful.

129
00:14:56,060 --> 00:14:59,140
I was just asking you to look into it.

130
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:07,700
From now on, I have to know who my enemies are.

131
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:11,380
Young Master, how long has it been?

132
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:16,530
Young Gyu, I heard that you used your hand this time.
(Lee Bang Gan: Lee Seong Gye's fourth son)

133
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:18,170
Pardon?

134
00:15:18,930 --> 00:15:20,830
Jeong Mong Joo.

135
00:15:20,830 --> 00:15:22,420
Ah, yes.

136
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:25,710
You did well. Good job!

137
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:30,340
When you were hitting his head, it felt good, right?

138
00:15:30,340 --> 00:15:32,040
Ah, yes.

139
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:35,410
Where is Bang Won?

140
00:15:40,310 --> 00:15:48,470
What is this? Does this make sense?

141
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:56,700
How can Po Eun's end be like this?

142
00:15:56,700 --> 00:16:04,640
Yes, Teacher. How, under the heavens, can something like this happen?

143
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:09,020
If you do that in a place like this, everyone will misunderstand.

144
00:16:09,020 --> 00:16:10,880
You bastard!

145
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:18,150
Do you think you will be safe after doing this to Po Eun?

146
00:16:18,150 --> 00:16:20,330
I don't think I will be safe.

147
00:16:20,330 --> 00:16:25,650
Also, I've never wished for a safe life.

148
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:37,460
You will face a more merciless fate than Po Eun.

149
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:43,840
Your end will be more horrendous than Po Eun's.

150
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:46,870
Yes. It might be that way

151
00:16:46,870 --> 00:16:52,280
but you won't see it, Teacher.

152
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:57,300
You don't have much time left.

153
00:17:14,540 --> 00:17:18,660
Tell the person who is writing the impeachment list to include Woo Hak Joo.

154
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:21,060
Woo Hak Joo is already on it.

155
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:25,560
Yesterday, you told me to add Lee Jung Hak, Ho Hong Soo, Lee Sung In, Kim Jin Yang, and Woo Hak Joo.

156
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:29,600
Is that so? Then there are 56 people.

157
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:33,100
They cannot be allowed to stay in Gaegyeong before the coronation--

158
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:35,140
It must not happen.

159
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:38,530
Are you okay? What's the matter?

160
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:43,600
It's nothing. I'm okay.

161
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:46,660
Do you think you'll be able to eat your meal?

162
00:17:46,660 --> 00:17:51,510
I have to eat. Even through gritted teeth, I have to eat.

163
00:17:59,430 --> 00:18:02,320
He's probably having a hard time even if he acts like he's not.

164
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:04,100
Go ahead.

165
00:18:12,450 --> 00:18:15,310
Please give us rice porridge here.

166
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:17,310
Yes. Go inside.

167
00:18:17,310 --> 00:18:18,560
Let's go in.

168
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:21,150
I'm fine.

169
00:18:21,150 --> 00:18:22,910
Okay.

170
00:18:37,050 --> 00:18:39,370
Elder Sam Bong.

171
00:18:47,970 --> 00:18:50,030
It's been a while.

172
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:55,010
Yeon Hyang! The little court lady!

173
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:06,500
Just like how you are not just a young scholar anymore, I am no longer a little court lady.

174
00:19:08,590 --> 00:19:11,230
Just what happened?

175
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:13,730
You have changed a lot.

176
00:19:13,730 --> 00:19:16,850
What's going on?

177
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:21,730
Are you... Nameless?

178
00:19:21,730 --> 00:19:23,670
That's right.

179
00:19:25,460 --> 00:19:29,540
Do you know that your children are looking for you? Outside... Your child is outside.

180
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:32,620
I know. Please don't call him.

181
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:33,840
How?

182
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:38,560
I came here today to only talk to you.

183
00:19:50,900 --> 00:19:54,500
Calm down. We only came for a talk

184
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:57,240
with your elder.

185
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,180
Who?

186
00:19:58,180 --> 00:20:00,360
Our side's Elder.

187
00:20:04,530 --> 00:20:08,020
You became faster.

188
00:20:08,020 --> 00:20:12,490
It must be great to be young. You're developing like this.

189
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:14,280
If you do anything to Elder...

190
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:18,070
I won't, so relax.

191
00:20:19,230 --> 00:20:22,610
If you fight me here,

192
00:20:22,610 --> 00:20:27,370
it might get even more dangerous. I'm not the only one you will be fighting.

193
00:20:27,370 --> 00:20:30,590
What was that sound from outside?

194
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:36,450
It seems like my bodyguard said hi.

195
00:20:37,330 --> 00:20:39,960
Nothing will happen.

196
00:20:42,230 --> 00:20:46,470
I guess the new country will be revealed soon.

197
00:20:47,610 --> 00:20:49,330
Are you against it?

198
00:20:49,330 --> 00:20:50,650
No.

199
00:20:50,650 --> 00:20:53,810
Then why are you blocking us?

200
00:20:53,810 --> 00:20:55,910
We weren't, in the beginning.

201
00:20:55,910 --> 00:21:00,950
When we heard about your plan, we were excited and cheered you on.

202
00:21:00,950 --> 00:21:05,530
We even tried to help, before we found out about that truth.

203
00:21:05,530 --> 00:21:08,610
Are you talking about the land reform?

204
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:11,170
The equal land division, the land distribution.

205
00:21:11,170 --> 00:21:15,950
Whatever the name, in the end the problem is the land reform.

206
00:21:17,190 --> 00:21:20,730
Didn't you already burn the land registers?

207
00:21:20,730 --> 00:21:25,310
Stop the process and forget about equally sharing lands, Elder.

208
00:21:26,570 --> 00:21:30,010
Your organization must have a lot of land.

209
00:21:30,010 --> 00:21:33,710
So you probably suffered some losses from it.

210
00:21:33,710 --> 00:21:42,590
Since there are a lot of people, a few of them have a lot of land, but the majority do not.

211
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,290
Then why?

212
00:21:44,290 --> 00:21:46,710
It's because of principle.

213
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:54,470
A person chases after work, and the generation chases after the person. That is our principle.

214
00:21:54,470 --> 00:21:59,470
But the new country denies this great desire.

215
00:21:59,470 --> 00:22:00,910
You say that it's great?

216
00:22:00,910 --> 00:22:06,890
The land reform fundamentally seals people off from any desire to have more land.

217
00:22:06,890 --> 00:22:12,190
That desire has brought Goryeo to this state. That personal land ownership.

218
00:22:12,190 --> 00:22:16,170
And so you are going to proceed with the land reform?

219
00:22:16,170 --> 00:22:19,090
Equally distributing land for every person,

220
00:22:19,090 --> 00:22:22,190
and not being able to increase this amount a little bit. This is what the land distribution does.

221
00:22:22,190 --> 00:22:25,550
Since no one is able to increase their land by even a little bit,

222
00:22:25,550 --> 00:22:28,890
no one will ever have their land taken by even a little bit.

223
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:35,590
We are the ones who first created the concept of personal land ownership.

224
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:40,870
A few hundred years ago, when it seemed only right that land belonged solely to king and country,

225
00:22:40,870 --> 00:22:45,750
we cultivated the wasteland and created the system of personal land ownership.

226
00:22:45,750 --> 00:22:46,990
And?

227
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:50,690
As a result of the people's desire to have their own land,

228
00:22:50,690 --> 00:22:53,170
they crazily ran to the wasteland and dug.

229
00:22:53,170 --> 00:22:57,050
After that the farmlands grew rapidly,

230
00:22:57,050 --> 00:23:00,470
and the Three Kingdoms became more prosperous than ever before.

231
00:23:00,470 --> 00:23:04,870
Desire paved a way and achieved prosperity.

232
00:23:04,870 --> 00:23:10,050
And what happened to that prosperity? Who are the ones that became prosperous?

233
00:23:10,050 --> 00:23:14,230
In the end, more than 70% of the country's land was taken by the Gwon Moon Sae Jok.

234
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:17,350
The people didn't even have the land to place a single nail, so they were kicked out from their homes

235
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:21,550
and slowly died away from starvation or slavery.

236
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:26,750
So is it really great? The desire for all this?

237
00:23:26,750 --> 00:23:32,030
A person perseveres through many hardships in order to expand their work.

238
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:38,010
As a result, in the past the world advanced and could have gone forward.

239
00:23:38,010 --> 00:23:40,970
The world from now on will be different.

240
00:23:41,750 --> 00:23:44,630
In the place of the desire to chase after work,

241
00:23:44,630 --> 00:23:47,390
Neo-Confucianist ideals will take precedent.

242
00:23:47,390 --> 00:23:49,910
A country where every person becomes a wise man.

243
00:23:49,910 --> 00:23:52,790
Therefore, a country will be made where no one groans for having theirs taken,

244
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:57,630
and no one takes another's in order to fill his own belly.

245
00:23:58,890 --> 00:24:01,250
It seems you aren't going to give up.

246
00:24:01,250 --> 00:24:06,450
Of course. From the trade and commerce on the outside to the marketplace on the inside,

247
00:24:06,450 --> 00:24:10,550
this desire will be controlled and managed by the nation so that

248
00:24:10,550 --> 00:24:16,870
the poison from desire will never cause us to hurt each other.

