428
00:41:23,330 --> 00:41:25,450
Then where could those scholars have gone?

429
00:41:25,450 --> 00:41:27,990
Those scholars?

430
00:41:27,990 --> 00:41:32,050
They were the scholars who put up posters about executing His Highness Bang Won, right?

431
00:41:32,050 --> 00:41:39,750
Yes. So I followed after them, and they were looking at these.

432
00:41:44,430 --> 00:41:47,170
This is a map...

433
00:41:48,470 --> 00:41:50,490
Tongsung Village...?

434
00:41:52,270 --> 00:41:55,810
