435
00:41:55,810 --> 00:42:00,130
There's barely anyone living there, so there's nothing to report.

436
00:42:00,870 --> 00:42:04,970
Doesn't it seem like there's going to be some kind of gathering?

437
00:42:04,970 --> 00:42:09,630
Boss! The assembly of the inspector general officials just ended.

438
00:42:09,630 --> 00:42:12,110
These are the names of the attendees.

439
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:13,710
Okay.

440
00:42:16,210 --> 00:42:19,830
You can write pretty well now.

441
00:42:19,830 --> 00:42:22,550
That's because you're teaching me well.

442
00:42:28,870 --> 00:42:32,750
Please have a look at this, Your Highness.

443
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:42,890
The scholars who wanted to execute Your Highness have been passing this to each other every night.

444
00:42:44,730 --> 00:42:47,130
Tongsong Village.

445
00:42:47,130 --> 00:42:51,550
It's outside the palace but it's not that far.

446
00:42:51,550 --> 00:42:53,970
Should I go there once?

447
00:42:53,970 --> 00:42:58,770
I don't know why I'm so nervous about the scholars' examination.

448
00:42:58,770 --> 00:43:03,030
Since you are like that, I feel the same.

449
00:43:04,210 --> 00:43:08,730
It's the first civil examination of this new country, so it's normal to be excited.

450
00:43:08,730 --> 00:43:15,110
It will all go well because Lord Sam Bong has prepared it while even skipping meals.

451
00:43:15,110 --> 00:43:20,490
