00:48:48,870 --> 00:48:52,590
They could be gathered somewhere planning something.

497
00:48:52,590 --> 00:48:53,950
What do you mean?

498
00:48:53,950 --> 00:48:59,510
There's no way of knowing that, but such a large number of people has disappeared in such a short time.

499
00:48:59,510 --> 00:49:02,110
Just what are they doing and where?

500
00:49:06,250 --> 00:49:09,430
I found out where they are and what they are doing.

501
00:49:09,430 --> 00:49:10,730
Where was it?

502
00:49:10,730 --> 00:49:14,010
They're on Mount Gwangdeok, West of Gaegyeong.

503
00:49:15,110 --> 00:49:17,230
What are they doing there?

504
00:49:17,230 --> 00:49:20,930
They gathered and are building a village.

505
00:49:22,050 --> 00:49:24,630
What are you saying? Say it in details

506
00:49:24,630 --> 00:49:28,730
There was a map being passed around between the scholars, so we chased after them.

507
00:49:28,730 --> 00:49:34,430
And when we went to Tongsung Village in Mount Gwangdeok,

508
00:49:34,430 --> 00:49:36,270
everyone took off their traditional hats and scholar hoods,

509
00:49:36,270 --> 00:49:40,650
and went to the village after donning straw hats.

510
00:49:40,650 --> 00:49:42,690
Gwaegwan.

511
00:49:44,770 --> 00:49:50,030
This is their demonstration that they do not approve the government and the king.

512
00:49:50,030 --> 00:49:51,770
We can't just let this be.

513
00:49:51,770 --> 00:49:53,990
We can only stay still.

514
00:49:55,090 --> 00:49:58,030
It's not illegal so we can't reprimand them,

515
00:49:58,030 --> 00:50:03,530
but such movements can be critical at a time like this.

516
00:50:03,530 --> 00:50:08,790
When the news spreads, more people will join them, and as you saw at the civil exam,

517
00:50:08,790 --> 00:50:12,890
we won't be able to tell what kind of group actions they will take.

518
00:50:18,050 --> 00:50:19,290
What?

519
00:50:19,290 --> 00:50:25,230
It's not even enough that no one turned up for the examination. Now they are gathered to live there?

520
00:50:25,230 --> 00:50:26,850
Yes.

521
00:50:28,490 --> 00:50:32,790
The people call it Doomundong.

522
00:50:32,790 --> 00:50:34,270
Doomundong?

523
00:50:34,270 --> 00:50:36,570
It must mean a village outside the gate.

524
00:50:36,570 --> 00:50:38,930
I've never seen such bastards before!

525
00:50:38,930 --> 00:50:42,770
We can't just leave them alone like that, right outside the capital.

526
00:50:42,770 --> 00:50:48,750
Yes that is so. If they try to create some kind of conspiracy

527
00:50:48,750 --> 00:50:51,450
there's no telling what might happen.

528
00:50:51,450 --> 00:50:53,930
Let's send the troops.

529
00:50:55,090 --> 00:50:57,210
I'm saying we should bring them all in.

530
00:50:57,210 --> 00:50:59,450
For what crime?

531
00:50:59,450 --> 00:51:04,490
What do you mean what crime? The crime for despising the royal family, and disturbing the country.

532
00:51:04,490 --> 00:51:09,850
It's not like they caused a commotion, or sent petitions.

533
00:51:09,850 --> 00:51:15,990
Since we even declared rule by law, system and ordinance,

534
00:51:15,990 --> 00:51:17,910
it's not right for us to do that.

535
00:51:17,910 --> 00:51:22,450
But if we leave them be, more people will gather in Doomundong.

536
00:51:22,450 --> 00:51:26,820
That by itself will become a representation of denying the new dynasty.

537
00:51:30,660 --> 00:51:34,940
Doomundong... Doomundong...

538
00:51:52,930 --> 00:51:57,590
We are moved to tears with gratitude for giving everyone in our family a royal nickname.

539
00:51:57,590 --> 00:52:00,690
What happened to Bang Woo and Bang Ui?

540
00:52:00,690 --> 00:52:05,250
Bang Ui is still in Ham Joo while Bang Woo Hyung-nim is not feeling well

541
00:52:05,250 --> 00:52:07,130
He is staying at Jebyeokdo.

542
00:52:07,130 --> 00:52:09,490
Is he still like that?

543
00:52:09,490 --> 00:52:11,600
I will make a visit to Hyung-nim.

544
00:52:11,600 --> 00:52:13,330
Okay.

545
00:52:14,070 --> 00:52:16,350
It's been a while, Bang Gan.

546
00:52:16,350 --> 00:52:18,580
How was the situation in Ham Joo?

547
00:52:18,580 --> 00:52:22,010
Yes. There's nothing wrong in Ham Joo.

548
00:52:22,010 --> 00:52:23,760
The North is also quiet.

549
00:52:23,760 --> 00:52:31,100
Okay. You have worked hard instead of your father and older brothers.

550
00:52:31,100 --> 00:52:35,960
What hard work did I do when Father, you...

551
00:52:38,900 --> 00:52:44,810
I heard that you are very concerned because the of civil exam incident and Doomundong.
(Lee Bang Gan - Prince Hwae Ahn, Lee Seong Gye's fourth son)

552
00:52:44,810 --> 00:52:47,220
I've been in discussions with the Do Dang for days

553
00:52:47,220 --> 00:52:49,590
but it's not an easy decision.

554
00:52:49,590 --> 00:52:51,700
Those people who do not fear the heavens,
(Lee Bang Gwa - Prince Yeon Ahn, second son)

555
00:52:51,700 --> 00:52:54,910
how could they just do that in front of the capital?

556
00:52:54,910 --> 00:52:58,930
Because their respected teacher became like that,

557
00:52:58,930 --> 00:53:02,380
they are probably saying they'll do something.

558
00:53:14,010 --> 00:53:15,940
It's been a while.

559
00:53:15,940 --> 00:53:18,170
Yes, Your Highness.

560
00:53:18,170 --> 00:53:21,930
It seems that His Majesty is deeply worried about the problem with Doomundong.

561
00:53:21,930 --> 00:53:26,310
Yes. Since they are people who should be the country's support,

562
00:53:26,310 --> 00:53:29,130
he must be feeling great regret.

563
00:53:30,740 --> 00:53:33,780
Is there something I can do to help?

564
00:53:34,820 --> 00:53:36,060
Your Highness would?

565
00:53:36,060 --> 00:53:37,470
Yes.

566
00:53:38,370 --> 00:53:40,600
I don't mean anything else.

567
00:53:40,600 --> 00:53:45,270
No matter how you look at it, my immature actions were the cause of it, so

568
00:53:45,270 --> 00:53:48,480
I'm thinking of helping out.

569
00:53:48,480 --> 00:53:51,920
I am very grateful that you would like to help out.

570
00:53:51,920 --> 00:53:54,390
But why do you want to help?

571
00:53:54,390 --> 00:53:57,580
I will persuade those people

572
00:53:57,580 --> 00:54:00,740
to come back. What do you think?

573
00:54:03,060 --> 00:54:05,140
I will persuade them.

574
00:54:05,140 --> 00:54:10,440
You, who killed Po Eun, will persuade the scholars and officials who resigned?

575
00:54:10,440 --> 00:54:12,840
Just what are you thinking?

576
00:54:12,840 --> 00:54:16,640
How will you persuade them?

577
00:54:16,640 --> 00:54:20,460
I will give it a try.

578
00:54:20,460 --> 00:54:24,440
Can you really do it, Your Highness?

579
00:54:24,440 --> 00:54:29,920
If I do my best with sincerity, wouldn't it lead to a good result?

580
00:54:29,920 --> 00:54:33,840
Yes. Since you've decided to fix what you did yourself,

581
00:54:33,840 --> 00:54:36,550
I think it would be good to step up and do it yourself.

582
00:54:36,550 --> 00:54:41,830
At a time when a new country has just been established, a place like Doomundong must not exist.

583
00:54:41,830 --> 00:54:43,090
Yes.

584
00:54:43,090 --> 00:54:48,770
But I won't be able to persuade all of the hundreds of scholars who are there.

585
00:54:48,870 --> 00:54:51,130
I will persuade those I can.

586
00:54:51,130 --> 00:54:57,230
As for those who I cannot persuade, I will at least not let them stay at Doomundong.

587
00:54:57,230 --> 00:55:01,950
If you can do that, it will be a big help to the nation.

588
00:55:01,950 --> 00:55:05,510
Then, I beg of you.

589
00:55:13,820 --> 00:55:16,970
What are you going to do?

590
00:55:16,970 --> 00:55:21,160
The people who are in Doomundong think of you as an enemy.

591
00:55:21,160 --> 00:55:24,460
How will you persuade those people?

592
00:55:24,460 --> 00:55:29,640
With hard work and sincerity.

593
00:55:29,640 --> 00:55:31,620
Husband.

594
00:55:40,170 --> 00:55:44,890
Are you trying to change His Majesty's cold feelings towards you?

595
00:55:44,890 --> 00:55:49,110
If the person who killed Po Eun can change those people's hearts,

596
00:55:49,110 --> 00:55:51,650
this will become a symbolic event

597
00:55:51,650 --> 00:55:54,670
But how?

598
00:56:00,950 --> 00:56:03,990
Do you have a plan?

599
00:56:08,450 --> 00:56:13,430
An intelligent Prince wouldn't be acting like this without a plan in mind.

600
00:56:16,680 --> 00:56:21,180
Well since it seems like there will soon be a crown prince proclamation,

601
00:56:21,180 --> 00:56:24,880
before that you'll have to calm His Majesty's heart, right?

602
00:56:28,980 --> 00:56:31,240
It's western wind.

603
00:56:33,170 --> 00:56:36,190
Bang Won will persuade them?

604
00:56:36,190 --> 00:56:37,280
Yes.

605
00:56:37,280 --> 00:56:41,590
If we can persuade them, nothing could be better than that.

606
00:56:41,590 --> 00:56:45,380
Even if he can't, in showing his sincerity

607
00:56:45,380 --> 00:56:47,630
there will be no harm.

608
00:56:47,630 --> 00:56:52,530
Prince Jeong An (Lee Bang Won) already left for today so please wait.

609
00:56:55,130 --> 00:56:59,210
We will be going to the West Gate of Doomundong so go to the East Gate.

610
00:56:59,210 --> 00:57:00,460
Yes!

611
00:57:00,460 --> 00:57:02,110
Let's go!

612
00:57:06,640 --> 00:57:10,680
Since Prince Jeong An is not scared of difficult and complicated things,

613
00:57:10,680 --> 00:57:13,580
it's worth expecting something from it.

614
00:57:16,040 --> 00:57:20,480
Is he trying to gain merit to earn my forgiveness?

615
00:57:20,480 --> 00:57:24,370
Do that. If you do...

616
00:57:24,370 --> 00:57:26,010
You bastard!

617
00:57:26,010 --> 00:57:28,020
Hey!

618
00:57:38,200 --> 00:57:43,540
You killed Teacher Po Eun. What nerve do you have to come here?

619
00:57:44,460 --> 00:57:48,920
We don't feel like listening to even a word of your excuse.

620
00:57:48,920 --> 00:57:52,260
I don't make any excuses.

621
00:57:52,260 --> 00:57:54,960
Then, why are you here?!

622
00:57:54,960 --> 00:57:56,960
Set it on fire!

623
00:57:59,210 --> 00:58:02,130
What? Set it on fire?

624
00:58:02,130 --> 00:58:07,090
What was that? Didn't you say you'll persuade them?

625
00:58:07,090 --> 00:58:10,750
I will persuade them when they come out.

626
00:58:12,130 --> 00:58:16,250
There will be those who come out and those who'll be burned in the fire.

627
00:58:16,250 --> 00:58:19,370
I will only take and persuade those who come out.

628
00:58:19,370 --> 00:58:20,760
Your Highness!

629
00:58:20,760 --> 00:58:25,710
This is my way and my place.

630
00:58:25,710 --> 00:58:31,190
How would I rise up without touching this field of shit when it's a field of shit I've fallen in?

631
00:58:36,870 --> 00:58:40,910
Father, and also teacher Sam Bong,

632
00:58:40,910 --> 00:58:42,850
you'll see.

633
00:58:42,850 --> 00:58:46,390
I will build power in my own way.

634
00:58:46,390 --> 00:58:51,230
Even if I were to die and live again, I believe I'm right.

635
00:58:51,230 --> 00:58:55,770
I might find my way by doing this.

636
00:58:55,770 --> 00:58:57,510
What are you doing?!

637
00:58:57,510 --> 00:59:01,150
Set it on fire! Right now!

638
00:59:28,700 --> 00:59:30,480
Six Flying Dragons

639
00:59:30,480 --> 00:59:32,790
You bastard! Do you not even fear the heavens?

640
00:59:32,790 --> 00:59:34,740
They're still overflowing with strength.

641
00:59:34,740 --> 00:59:37,800
Your Highness, Prince Jeong An has disappeared.

642
00:59:37,800 --> 00:59:39,810
The rule of primogeniture has been broken!

643
00:59:39,810 --> 00:59:41,440
Come in.

644
00:59:41,440 --> 00:59:44,560
He has to become the king no matter what.

645
00:59:44,560 --> 00:59:47,540
What about making Prince Ui An the Crown Prince?
(Prince Ui An: Lee Bang Seok)

646
00:59:47,540 --> 00:59:50,650
Crown Prince. Crown Prince, you say?
